  95:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/timers.c ****  * two message types are defined in two separate structures, xTimerParametersType
  96:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/timers.c ****  * and xCallbackParametersType respectively. */
